channel.title: Batch Compiler - No more leeched batch file codes as in server compilers
channel.description:
If you are sick of people 'leeching' your lines of commands that you made yourself?
Ever heard of a Batch Compiler?
I have found a reallly good one after searching for a while.
Theres a couple of things that you can do like you can change the icon and just mess around with the program.
This is the installer: [url=http://uppit.com/HNKO03]http://uppit.com/HNKO03[/url]
Here are the directions in picture:
[IMG]http://i38.tinypic.com/b835hy.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i35.tinypic.com/w2g2na.jpg[/img]
any questions just ask...
